description:
HIS EYE IS ON THE SPARROW "Karaoke" (Jennifer LaMountain Style)

In this fun and easy gospel karaoke video, I'll be performing His Eye is on the Sparrow by Jennifer LaMountain. This classic gospel song is perfect for a night of fun with friends, and I promise you'll have a great time singing along!
If you're looking for a fun and easy way to entertain yourself on a weekend night, then check out this gospel karaoke video! I'll be performing His Eye is on the Sparrow in a style that will make you want to get up and sing along!
